{
  "stem": "15082.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In March, what had happened is on a Sunday, you could hear that the front were coming closer, the shooting that went on between the Germans and the Russians.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Russians were advancing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Of course, we were-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Marczeniek fed us all this, because we couldn't see it or hear it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were not communicating with anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he says, he thinks that it's almost the end is coming, that we will be freed shortly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] We were afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was afraid that they were going to burn the village, because he heard what they were doing in other villages, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was afraid that we might get burned in that thing, because he was a rich Polish farmer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they may take it out on him at the end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We went from his farmhouse into the forest, which was maybe 1,000 feet away, Sunday morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some Germans cavalry spotted us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they started chasing after us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But luckily, there was a ravine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it was in March.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was very muddy and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Their horses got into mud.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they couldn't catch us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "On foot, we did better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we, again, ran into the forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And it was that-- that was the Sunday before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So, finally, nothing happened to the village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We came back Sunday night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We returned to the farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we had dinner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And, again, he took us in there, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] talked to us about it, what had happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And he says, it's imminent that it's-- they could see by the movement and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "The following Sunday, the Ukrainians assembled all Pollocks into that ravine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And one of them was his wife.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
